{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/bannerSteamUltra.gif?t=1736847332\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FEATURES\u00a0</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build a deck of heroes from Greek mythology\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose one of the five Deities, each one with their own power\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Obtain new spells, enhancements, and hero cards to conquer more realms\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Classical art by world-renowned painters like John Waterhouse and Frederic Leighton\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Compete on the Online Leaderboard\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Power of the Gods</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become a Greek Deity and build a deck of heroes, spells, and enhancements to compete with others on the Global Leaderboard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/steamPageGifSPellEffects.gif?t=1736847332\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Strategy and Synergy</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hone your deck-building skills to conquer as many realms as possible. Your starting deck can be modified in tons of ways to create interesting builds synergizing with each of the five deities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/BossesNoNumbers.gif?t=1736847332\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Ascend Divinity</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet the Blind Poet between conquered realms to modify your deck with new cards. Defeat rival Deities who dare summon themselves to the board, and claim their power to ascend Olympus!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/ShowcaseC.gif?t=1736847332\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Life and Legacy</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Anticipate your enemies and manage your token economy, watch each hero's golden lotus closely\u2014 when the final petal falls, the hero will perish. Yet their legacy inspires the strength of those who will come after.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/extras/bannerSteamUltra.gif?t=1736847332\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736847332","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/page.bg.jpg?t=1736847332","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/95dcc3c393b6e11843b221eb7c9e8ccdee488a1b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736847332","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684510/95dcc3c393b6e11843b221eb7c9e8ccdee488a1b/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736847332","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"The game features classical artworks depicting gods by artists like John William Waterhouse and Frederic Leighton. \r\n\r\nThese works, notorious for their artistic merit, have long been celebrated in museums and other forms of media. \r\n\r\nI hope this will help evoke the experience of viewing art in a gallery for the players."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/26845